Subject: [PATCH] Fix shorts SQL injection, password_gen bugs, and wire up
 badape Reddit API

- modules/sql.py: replace all f-string SQL with parameterized queries (%s)
- app/shorts/routes.py: add missing os import, fix invalid error redirects,
  extract domain to constant
- app/password_gen/routes.py: fix complicate_word (no longer loses substitution),
  fix addCap (no longer returns inside loop), fix randint off-by-one,
  remove thread-unsafe global lastnum
- app/badape/routes.py: implement Reddit API integration for ShillPoints counter
  (r/Superstonk karma from last 1000 posts + 1000 comments)
- app/templates/badape/badape.html: remove archived notice, add error display

Reddit env vars needed: reddit_client_id, reddit_client_secret, reddit_user_agent

